{"tid":2385033,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再用bitlocker","createTime":"2021-01-28T22:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T19:25:03.000Z","uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3d72b035a63b5be738d2174cd4a5e04a8dbf79aa","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://secret.club/2021/01/15/bitlocker-bypass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecret.club%2F2021%2F01%2F15%2Fbitlocker-bypass.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=faddad38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://secret.club/2021/01/15/bitlocker-bypass.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<em>Given a Windows 10 system without known passwords and a BitLocker-protected hard drive, an administrator account could be adding by doing the following:<br />\n<br />\n1. At the sign-in screen, select &ldquo;I have forgotten my password.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2. Bypass the lock and enable autoplay of removable drives.<br />\n<br />\n3. Insert a USB stick with my .exe and a junction folder.<br />\n<br />\n4 .Run executable.<br />\n<br />\n5 .Remove the thumb drive and put it back in again, go to the main screen.<br />\n<br />\n6 .From there launch narrator, that will execute a DLL payload planted earlier.<br />\n<br />\nNow a user account is added called hax with password &ldquo;hax&rdquo; with membership in Administrators. To update the list with accounts to log into, click I forgot my password and then return to the main screen.</em>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n6步就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n要用就用veracrypt<br />\n<br />\nDownload：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Downloads.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.veracrypt.fr%2Fen%2FDownloads.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=3f6a53a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Downloads.html</a><br />\n<br />\n點用：<a href=\"https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Beginner%27s%20Tutorial.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.veracrypt.fr%2Fen%2FBeginner%2527s%2520Tutorial.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=1677af3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.veracrypt.fr/en/Beginner%27s%20Tutorial.html</a>"},{"pid":"9cd647bd9365eb127eb446c1c2803251d63a48d5","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:13:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"742e3bfa5a4ae789c69177c4f4ae515a065f1e24","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:13:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68b46d2f1958538f5174bf2295ac887254340f41","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:13:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a2e57ef8cebd3deddbcc61de01df1ce023522554","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:14:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a7f7f64e080880735a8f9da43b9eba4251b5192b","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:22:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee403d4f9f1fec6e23f80c7f5c19eef840fc2434","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:53:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2afa4d96b770abfad2630773c1c068c136ab2490","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:54:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e53a0f0f12758a8c31195d01f44094df50a7cea7","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:54:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3887e00bb3aff426052a79725af134a7bb4b5205","tid":2385033,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b59fe4b65a420ffa6bbffc6ad01b4c5ca402cf","tid":2385033